  "detailed_description": "<h1>Just Updated</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/3dc0a2ac2b6deabacd530ce44717996c.avif?t=1774417533\" width=960 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We have released a major update that diversifies how you explore the Garden of Witches. We’ve expanded combat progression and exploration, adding various game elements that will broaden your tactical choices. Experience new rooms, new enemies and spells, the new Imprint System and a completely overhauled combat system!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>New Monsters and New “Rush” Spell</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/1f28c87307de87a1f20543cc9fd5c475.poster.avif?t=1774417533\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/1f28c87307de87a1f20543cc9fd5c475.webm?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/1f28c87307de87a1f20543cc9fd5c475.mp4?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New monsters</strong> have been added to reduce repetitiveness and spice up how you battle your way through the Garden. Additionally, the new <strong>Rush</strong> spell gives you a new tactical option in your arsenal, allowing you to either quickly close the gap with enemies or escape dangerous situations.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Imprint System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/43c4eb579532ecd6df9d3766c1a4b1c0.avif?t=1774417533\" width=960 height=403 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Imprints </strong>have been added as a new mechanic that expands how you can develop and personalize your builds. Imprints enhance or even fundamentally change how you can utilize your Scissors, Spells and Special Skills. Using Imprints, you can create distinct playstyles and unique combat strategies even with the same Armory loadout.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>New Rooms to Navigate</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/8207ef126f8d66fc49989b56acc6e4ea.poster.avif?t=1774417533\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/8207ef126f8d66fc49989b56acc6e4ea.webm?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/8207ef126f8d66fc49989b56acc6e4ea.mp4?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New rooms such as<strong> Curse</strong>, <strong>Well</strong> and <strong>Elite Monster Rooms</strong> have been added to diversify the types of encounters you’ll face as you navigate through the Garden. Each room impacts your build and gameplay in different ways, increasing the strategic importance of your pathing and decision-making on the map.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Armory Loadouts</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/a3a7a6500f7be0e63289140b04bd7db8.poster.avif?t=1774417533\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/a3a7a6500f7be0e63289140b04bd7db8.webm?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/a3a7a6500f7be0e63289140b04bd7db8.mp4?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Armory’s functionality has been expanded, allowing you to pre-select your choice of Scissors, Spells and Runes before starting a run. Now, you can prepare your desired loadout before leaving home and jump into battle with greater ease!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Combat System Overhaul</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/fc73f34dd75ec6970fad3a6dbf626b1b.avif?t=1774417533\" width=960 height=540 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Spell, Attribute, and Relic Systems have undergone a comprehensive overhaul. This new structure allows for even more diverse build combinations and unique playstyles.</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/1f28c87307de87a1f20543cc9fd5c475.poster.avif?t=1774417533\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/1f28c87307de87a1f20543cc9fd5c475.webm?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/1f28c87307de87a1f20543cc9fd5c475.mp4?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Garden of Witches</strong> is a fast-paced action roguelike where you’ll experience exhilarating combat, precise mechanics, and the thrill of crafting powerful synergies. To beat the game, you’ll need to prepare carefully, master enemy patterns, and strike with style. Shape your build from a randomized pool of spells, upgrades, and relics, and outsmart the other witches that stand in your way.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Host a Tea Party with Witches</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Garden is slowly deteriorating, and it’s all thanks to the idle and selfish witches who’ve lost their sense of duty. To save the Garden, you must beat some sense into them and round them up for the tea party.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/77d147a95ebb4b2952d7a8b2d88ec6ac.poster.avif?t=1774417533\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/77d147a95ebb4b2952d7a8b2d88ec6ac.webm?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/77d147a95ebb4b2952d7a8b2d88ec6ac.mp4?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Enchanted Garden of Witches</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A fading sanctuary. Rebellious witches. Secrets hidden behind the curtain of dreams. Emotional graphics and immersive storytelling breathe life into a world on the verge of collapse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/7cf50734b3d9a03b38981f24144357b3.poster.avif?t=1774417533\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/7cf50734b3d9a03b38981f24144357b3.webm?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/7cf50734b3d9a03b38981f24144357b3.mp4?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Strategy, Synergy, and Style</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Sil, the Thread Witch. Wield giant scissors to protect your precious sanctuary and persuade the other unruly witches to gather for the tea party. After each battle, you’ll face critical decisions, choosing spells, upgrades, and relics that define your playstyle. Harness the mysterious power of witches and “persuade” the other witches in the garden with your own unique and strategic combat style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/43c2ae6b77d5854014c0b6a0440d1705.poster.avif?t=1774417533\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/43c2ae6b77d5854014c0b6a0440d1705.webm?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/43c2ae6b77d5854014c0b6a0440d1705.mp4?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How to Convince a Witch</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every witch has distinct attack patterns, and they won’t go down easily. Study their movements, time your counterattacks, and use everything in your arsenal to win them over. Precision and quick thinking are your keys to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/77d147a95ebb4b2952d7a8b2d88ec6ac.poster.avif?t=1774417533\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/77d147a95ebb4b2952d7a8b2d88ec6ac.webm?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/77d147a95ebb4b2952d7a8b2d88ec6ac.mp4?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What Matters is an Unyielding Heart</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even if you hit a wall, don’t give up! Each death is a step forward, unlocking new abilities and permanent growth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/7c1f87f7b612cba1e97ac3cea05eb236.poster.avif?t=1774417533\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/7c1f87f7b612cba1e97ac3cea05eb236.webm?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/7c1f87f7b612cba1e97ac3cea05eb236.mp4?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Early Access</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the current Early Access version, you can enjoy the following content:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The full main story (5 chapters)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A deep combat system built on flexible attribute-based builds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A progression system that highlights strategic elements such as attribute synergies, relics, and weapon variations as you progress through each chapter</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Light endgame content focused on record achievement</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Looking ahead, we plan on adding new areas, bosses, endgame content, and a variety of additional features one by one. We’re committed to delivering a game experience that continually evolves with consistent updates and improvements until our game is ready for its 1.0 release.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your feedback will shape the future of our game. We hope you will join us and be a part of the journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/3e6d08f70dd6a261d4a53f3f1bd6ca80.avif?t=1774417533\" width=600 height=427 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/1f28c87307de87a1f20543cc9fd5c475.poster.avif?t=1774417533\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/1f28c87307de87a1f20543cc9fd5c475.webm?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/1f28c87307de87a1f20543cc9fd5c475.mp4?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Garden of Witches</strong> is a fast-paced action roguelike where you’ll experience exhilarating combat, precise mechanics, and the thrill of crafting powerful synergies. To beat the game, you’ll need to prepare carefully, master enemy patterns, and strike with style. Shape your build from a randomized pool of spells, upgrades, and relics, and outsmart the other witches that stand in your way.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Host a Tea Party with Witches</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Garden is slowly deteriorating, and it’s all thanks to the idle and selfish witches who’ve lost their sense of duty. To save the Garden, you must beat some sense into them and round them up for the tea party.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/77d147a95ebb4b2952d7a8b2d88ec6ac.poster.avif?t=1774417533\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/77d147a95ebb4b2952d7a8b2d88ec6ac.webm?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/77d147a95ebb4b2952d7a8b2d88ec6ac.mp4?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Enchanted Garden of Witches</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A fading sanctuary. Rebellious witches. Secrets hidden behind the curtain of dreams. Emotional graphics and immersive storytelling breathe life into a world on the verge of collapse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/7cf50734b3d9a03b38981f24144357b3.poster.avif?t=1774417533\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/7cf50734b3d9a03b38981f24144357b3.webm?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/7cf50734b3d9a03b38981f24144357b3.mp4?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Strategy, Synergy, and Style</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Sil, the Thread Witch. Wield giant scissors to protect your precious sanctuary and persuade the other unruly witches to gather for the tea party. After each battle, you’ll face critical decisions, choosing spells, upgrades, and relics that define your playstyle. Harness the mysterious power of witches and “persuade” the other witches in the garden with your own unique and strategic combat style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/43c2ae6b77d5854014c0b6a0440d1705.poster.avif?t=1774417533\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/43c2ae6b77d5854014c0b6a0440d1705.webm?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/43c2ae6b77d5854014c0b6a0440d1705.mp4?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How to Convince a Witch</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every witch has distinct attack patterns, and they won’t go down easily. Study their movements, time your counterattacks, and use everything in your arsenal to win them over. Precision and quick thinking are your keys to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/77d147a95ebb4b2952d7a8b2d88ec6ac.poster.avif?t=1774417533\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/77d147a95ebb4b2952d7a8b2d88ec6ac.webm?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/77d147a95ebb4b2952d7a8b2d88ec6ac.mp4?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What Matters is an Unyielding Heart</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even if you hit a wall, don’t give up! Each death is a step forward, unlocking new abilities and permanent growth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/7c1f87f7b612cba1e97ac3cea05eb236.poster.avif?t=1774417533\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/7c1f87f7b612cba1e97ac3cea05eb236.webm?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/7c1f87f7b612cba1e97ac3cea05eb236.mp4?t=1774417533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Early Access</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the current Early Access version, you can enjoy the following content:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The full main story (5 chapters)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A deep combat system built on flexible attribute-based builds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A progression system that highlights strategic elements such as attribute synergies, relics, and weapon variations as you progress through each chapter</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Light endgame content focused on record achievement</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Looking ahead, we plan on adding new areas, bosses, endgame content, and a variety of additional features one by one. We’re committed to delivering a game experience that continually evolves with consistent updates and improvements until our game is ready for its 1.0 release.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your feedback will shape the future of our game. We hope you will join us and be a part of the journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530470/extras/3e6d08f70dd6a261d4a53f3f1bd6ca80.avif?t=1774417533\" width=600 height=427 /></span></p>",
